+ Access Control\nLists (ACLs)
++ Privileges
+++_ SELECT, MODIFY, MANAGE
+++_ CREATE TABLE, USE SCHEMA
+++_ ALL PRIVILEGES (all applicable)
+++_ Object-specific validity
++ Securables
+++_ Metastore → Catalog → Schema
+++_ Table / View / Function / Volume
+++_ External locations
+++_ Hierarchical inheritance
++ Principals
+++_ User (e.g. alice@company.com)
+++_ Service Principal (app ID)
+++_ Group (recommended for mgmt)
+++_ Account users (all account users)
-- Entra ID Integration
---_ All identities in Entra ID
---_ Groups synced to Databricks
---_ Coordinate with Entra admins
@endmindmap
